commit.message: Bump to 0.13.2.5

Bump QuickCheck upper bound
More detailed failure, and fixed test case.

Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/bos/attoparsec

and add a test case for takeWhileIncluding.

Add `parseOnly` versions for lazy input

Previously, `Data.Attoparsec.ByteString.Lazy` just reexported
`Data.Attoparsec.ByteString.parseOnly`, which only accepts strict input;
same for `Data.Attoparsec.Text.Lazy`.

Closes: #143
